OL,3,CCampaigner 'disgusted' that assisted
OL,4,Cdying bill runs out of time
OL,6,F20-year-old Noah from Chepstow who has
OL,7,Fan inoperable brain tumour said he is
OL,8,F"disgusted" by the House of Lords,
OL,9,Farguing "they have had so long to sort
OL,10,Fit out, they have had so long to go
OL,11,Fthrough it".
OL,13,F"I don't want to see people suffering,
OL,14,FI don't want to see people going
OL,15,Fthrough this. I want people to have
OL,16,Fthe option to use it, and if push
OL,17,Fcomes to shove then if I need to use
OL,18,Fit one day, I want to be able to use
OL,19,Fit" he added.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
