PN,46906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777392670
OL,3,CCampaigner 'disgusted' that assisted
OL,4,Cdying bill runs out of time
OL,6,F"The Bill as it was drafted, and it
OL,7,Fhasn't changed a huge amount either,
OL,8,Fhas been from the outset very vague,
OL,9,Fand it leaves a lot of very important
OL,10,Ftopics like mental capacity
OL,11,Fassessments, assessing people for
OL,12,Fsuicidality for instance and also
OL,13,Fvulnerabilities like coercion,
OL,14,Fdomestic abuse etc."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
